title: CONNIE L. GREENE
maintext: CONNIE L. GREENE, 71, of Ashland, wife of Alger Greene, died Feb. 4 in the Hospice Care Center. Funeral service will be 1 p.m. Friday, Westwood Freewill Baptist Church. Burial will follow in Rose Hill Burial Park. Visitation will be from 11:30 a.m. to 1 p.m. Friday at the church. Arrangements are under the direction of Miller Funeral Home. www.mfhfuneralhome.com.
